ALETHEION_ENVIRONMENTAL_CLIMATE_INTEGRATION !ecologically-restorative! ENABLED

CONFIGURE MODULE EnvironmentalClimateIntegrationProfile
FOR PhoenixMetro.DesertGrid
NAMESPACE github.com/Doctor0Evil/Aletheion
DOMAIN ClimateAdaptive.Phoenix
ISOLATION BioSecure.Enclave
AUDIT CAS.Immutable.AppendOnly
RIGHTS Human AugmentedCitizen BiosignalCollector AkimelOodhamNation PiipaashNation WatershedEntity SonoranFloraCollective
CONSENT Visual Haptic Cognitive RegionNodes
THROTTLE ClimateAction.Spend.Guardrails
NONTRAIN ENFORCED
RETENTION AuditLogs.7d_Min Biosignals.24h_Max
TOKEN LeastPrivilege ShortLived
WATER Reclamation99Percent PureWaterPhoenix AquiferRechargeMonitored
HEAT CoolPavement12F AlbedoOptimized UrbanHeatIslandMitigation
MONSOON FlashFloodCapture2.71in StormwaterHarvesting HumidityCollectionAugSep
DUST HaboobDetectionADOT PM2.5PM10Sensors RealTimeHealthAlerts
FLORA SonoranNative SaguaroPaloVerdeOcotillo WildlifeCorridors
ZERO-WASTE MaterialLifecycle99Percent DemolitionToResource OrganicToEnergy
CROSSLANG RustEdge CppMachinery LuaAutomation KotlinCitizenApp

// ============================================================================
// INDIGENOUS TERRITORY & BIOTIC TREATY CONSTRAINTS (HARD BLOCKS)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (P): Node-Placement opportunities where civil-disturbance will-not create unrest.
// Per Rule (I): DID-Bound brain-identity (BI) and biosignal-collector respect.

DEFINE OBJECT IndigenousTerritoryConstraint
  ATTRIBUTES
    - NationPrimary        "Akimel O'odham"
    - NationSecondary      "Piipaash"
    - LanguageCode         "O'odham"
    - LandAcknowledgment   "Himad Dak Do'ag" (We Are All Together)
    - ConsultationRequired TRUE
    - TreatyViolationAction HALT_AND_NOTIFY
    - BioticRightsEnabled  TRUE

PROCEDURE TreatyCheckLifecycle
  1. VERIFY ActorID holds ValidDID_Bound_BrainIdentity
  2. CHECK TerritoryMetadata MATCHES IndigenousTerritoryConstraint
  3. IF ConsultationStatus != VerifiedConsent THEN HALT_ACTION LOG_TreatyViolation
  4. IF BioticImpactScore > Threshold THEN REQUIRE WatershedEntity_Consent
  5. RECORD ConsentHash INTO AuditChain (Aletheion_PQ_Secure_Reference)
  END TreatyCheckLifecycle

// ============================================================================
// CLIMATE ACTION THRESHOLDS (Phoenix-Specific Data 2025-2026)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (E): Desert-climate optimization, Monsoon resilience, Air quality.

DEFINE OBJECT ClimateThresholds
  ATTRIBUTES
    - MaxOperationalTempF  120.0
    - CoolPavementTriggerF 105.0
    - CoolPavementReductionF 12.0
    - MonsoonCaptureThresholdIn 2.71
    - DustAlertPM10        150.0
    - DustAlertPM25        55.0
    - WaterReclaimTargetPct 99.0
    - MinSoilMoisturePct   15.0
    - AquiferRechargeRateGPM 500.0
    - HumidityCaptureMinPct 40.0

// ============================================================================
// ACTION ATOM DEFINITIONS (Unified Governance Currency)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (L): High-density codes, syntax_ladders, cross-language program-ops.

DEFINE OBJECT ClimateActionAtom
  ATTRIBUTES
    - AtomID               UUIDv8_PostQuantum
    - RepoNamespace        github.com/Doctor0Evil/Aletheion
    - CommitHash           Aletheion_PQ_Secure_Hash
    - ActorID              DID_Bound_BrainIdentity
    - Capability           Enum(WaterReclaim, CoolPavement, MonsoonCapture, DustAlert, FloraCorridor, ZeroWaste)
    - ConsentClass         Enum(Visual, Haptic, Cognitive, RegionNodes)
    - RightsGuards         List(Human, AugmentedCitizen, BiosignalCollector, WatershedEntity)
    - ContextData          Struct(ClimateContext)
    - BudgetThrottle       Float(USD_Equivalent_Or_ResourceUnits)
    - TimestampUTC         Uint64

STRUCT ClimateContext
  FIELDS
    - SectorID             Uint32
    - AirTempF             Float32
    - PavementTempF        Float32
    - RainfallInch         Float32
    - HumidityPct          Float32
    - PM10_ug_m3           Float32
    - PM25_ug_m3           Float32
    - SoilMoisturePct      Float32
    - AquiferLevelFt       Float32
    - TerritoryHash        Uint128

// ============================================================================
// GOVERNANCE ENGINE LIFECYCLE (ERM Chain: Sense → Model → Treaty → Act)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (R): Turn research-data into valuable-code, vital-document.

PROCEDURE ClimateActionLifecycle
  1. VALIDATE Commit MATCH allow-listed climate modules (water-reclaim, heat-mitigate, monsoon-capture, dust-filter, flora-restore, zero-waste-flow)
     CHECK tests PASS rights-consent water-efficiency-99 heat-continuity-120F flood-capture-2.71 dust-pm10-alert flora-corridor
  2. REGISTER Artifact WITH RepoNamespace CommitHash ProfileVersion DeclaredCapabilities (water99, heat12, monsoon2.71, dustADOT, floraSonoran, waste99)
  3. ACQUIRELOCK key=phoenix-desert-climate-adaptive
  4. OPEN ClimateSandbox RUNTIME egressAllowList rateGuards seccompENFORCED heatProtocol120Fplus floodProtocolMonsoon dustProtocolHaboob
     EDGE Rust low-latency sensor fusion Cpp machinery control Lua script automation
  5. INVOKE ClimateActionAtom Input ActionAtom ConsentClass ContextMetadata (rainfall2.71, temp120, humidityMonsoon, pm10, dust, floraNode)
     ENFORCEMENT RightsGuards BudgetThrottle EcologicalRestore NodePlacementFairness civil-unrest-prevented industrial-installation-routes trash-collection-optimized high-toxicity-disposal-isolated
  6. DEPLOY NodeTypes water-reclaim-plant cool-pavement-surface monsoon-harvest-basin dust-sensor-array flora-corridor zero-waste-pipeline
     PLACEMENT fairness-win arche-definition rogue-pattern-prevented protest-strike-riot-avoided war-avoided
  7. RECORD ActionID RepoNamespace ActorID Doctor:JacobScottFarmer ConsentClass ResultCode Latency AffectedSectors (water, air, flora, waste, movement)
     PromptHash ConnectorID Timestamp INTO AuditChain
  8. OPTIMIZE RealTime biosignal-collector region-nodes bci-types citizen-movement agricultural-development urban-hygiene daily-habits
     INTEGRATE offline-capable offshore-indexing Github-adjustable
  9. VALIDATE PostAction water-reclaim-99 heat-reduce-12 monsoon-capture-full dust-alert-active flora-preserved waste-99-restore
     IF violation HALT LOG NOTIFY Compliance FREEZE capability set ELSE ForwardDeploy EcologicalRestore
  10. RELEASELOCK successful-commit
      PROPAGATE cross-language Rust-Cpp-Lua-Kotlin interop syntax-ladder new-grammar density-max per-line impact autonomous-factory-ready
  END ClimateActionLifecycle

// ============================================================================
// RIGHTS GUARDS & CONSENT PROTOCOLS (Neurorights & BioticTreaties)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (I): Speak on my-behalf... as-an organically-integrated augmented-citizen.
// Per Rule (R): Non-discriminatory respect for particular-use of this space.

DEFINE OBJECT RightsGuardProtocol
  ATTRIBUTES
    - HumanConsentRequired TRUE
    - AugmentedCitizenOptIn  TRUE
    - BioticEntityRepresentation TRUE (Watershed, Flora, Fauna)
    - NeurorightsProtection  NO_COGNITIVE_LOAD_WITHOUT_CONSENT
    - DataSovereignty        CITIZEN_CONTROLLED_EXPORT
    - PrivacyPreservation    ZERO_KNOWLEDGE_INFRASTRUCTURE

PROCEDURE ConsentOrchestration
  1. IDENTIFY AffectedSectors FROM ClimateContext
  2. QUERY RightsGuards LIST FOR ConsentStatus
  3. IF ConsentClass == Cognitive THEN CHECK BCI_Signal_StressLevel < Threshold
  4. IF ConsentClass == RegionNodes THEN CHECK WatershedEntity_HealthMetric > SafeLimit
  5. IF AnyGuard DENIES THEN HALT_ACTION LOG_ConsentViolation
  6. IF AllGuard APPROVES THEN PROCEED_TO_EXECUTION
  END ConsentOrchestration

// ============================================================================
// AUDIT & FORENSICS (Immutable, Post-Quantum Secure)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (R): No rollbacks, no digital twins, no fictional content.
// Per Rule (L): Reason-with circumstances-for: City-Planning, Build-Materials.

DEFINE OBJECT AuditChainSpec
  ATTRIBUTES
    - Structure            MerkleHashTree_PostQuantum
    - Immutability         ENFORCED_HARDWARE_TPM
    - RetentionPolicy      AuditLogs.7d_Min Signals.24h_Max
    - Accessibility        PUBLIC_READ_PRIVATE_WRITE
    - ForensicsReady       TRUE
    - IncidentResponse     AUTOMATED_BREACH_DETECTION_ISOLATION

PROCEDURE AuditLogging
  1. SERIALIZE ActionAtom + ActionResult
  2. HASH Payload USING Aletheion_PQ_Algo (No SHA/Blake/Argon/Keccak/Ripemd/XXH3)
  3. APPEND To Chain WITH PreviousHash Reference
  4. VERIFY Integrity CHECKSUM
  5. NOTIFY Compliance IF AnomalyDetected
  END AuditLogging

// ============================================================================
// CROSS-LANGUAGE INTEROP MAP (Syntax Ladders)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (L): Supported-language set: ALN, Lua, Rust, Javascript, Kotlin/Android, C++

DEFINE OBJECT CrossLanguageInterop
  MAPPINGS
    - RustEdge             sensor_fusion/src/lib.rs (Ingest, Validate, Fuse)
    - CppMachinery         machinery/control/src/climate_engine.cpp (Actuate, Control, Drive)
    - LuaAutomation        automation/scripts/v1/monsoon_orchestration.lua (Orchestrate, Schedule, Logic)
    - KotlinCitizenApp     citizen/interface/src/ConsentActivity.kt (Consent, Notify, Interface)
    - JavascriptDashboard  dashboard/web/src/climate_monitor.js (Visualize, Alert, Report)
    - ALNManifest          governance/manifests/environmental/v1/phoenix.desert.grid.climate.aln (Govern, Policy, Rule)

// ============================================================================
// EMERGENCY & FAILSAFE PROTOCOLS (Civil Unrest Prevention)
// ============================================================================
// Per Rule (P): Declare principles... where civil-disturbance... will-not create... unrest.

DEFINE OBJECT EmergencyFailsafe
  ATTRIBUTES
    - CivilUnrestDetection TRUE (SocialSignalMonitoring)
    - IndustrialRouteIsolation TRUE
    - ToxicityDisposalSafeZone TRUE
    - WarAvoidanceProtocol   ACTIVE
    - ProtestStrikeRiotPrevention TRUE

PROCEDURE EmergencyHalt
  1. DETECT SocialSignal_Anomaly OR Infrastructure_CriticalFailure
  2. HALT All Non-Essential ClimateActions
  3. MAINTAIN LifeSupport (Water, Air, Shade)
  4. NOTIFY Human Oversight + Indigenous Representatives
  5. LOCK Down Capability Set UNTIL Review Complete
  END EmergencyHalt

END ENVIRONMENTAL_CLIMATE_INTEGRATION
